|-
|幼童軍<br /><small>Cub Scout</small>||7<span style="font-size:smaller;">1/2</span>～12||colspan=3|幼童軍團<br /><small>Cub Scout Pack</small>
|-
|童軍<br /><small>Scout</small>||11～16||海童軍團<br /><small>Sea Scout Troop</small>||童軍團<br /><small>Scout Troop</small>||空童軍團<br /><small>Air Scout Troop</small>
